data.description: PRICE REDUCED &  SELLER OFFERING ONE YEAR HOME WARRANTY TO BUYER!! Welcome to 2012 Track Circle, a stunning 4-bedroom, 3 bath home that combines modern living with convenience in the heart of Fredericksburg. This beautifully appointed home offers a perfect blend of comfort and style.  Centrally located in Fredericksburg Park this like-new townhome faces a lovely common area complete with a meandering sidewalk which enhances the overall charm of the property.  The main living level is adorned with luxury vinyl plank flooring, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen boasts quartz countertops, bar seating, tile backsplash, and SS appliances.  From the kitchen, step outside onto the 10’x12’ composite deck , seamlessly extending the living space offering a perfect spot for evening entertaining or simply unwinding in the fresh air.  The luxurious owner's suite is a retreat within itself, featuring a full bath with a double bowl vanity and dual closets, offering both space and functionality. The three additional bedrooms are well-appointed and generously sized, providing flexibility for guests,  or a home office.  The fourth-floor loft adds a versatile touch to the home, providing an ideal space for a bedroom, home office, playroom, or additional living area to suit your lifestyle complete with its own full bath!  Convenience is key, and this home delivers. Take a short stroll to Alum Spring Park or the VCR Trail or easily access the VRE for a stress-free commute. Enjoy the convenience of being just moments away from shops and dining in Downtown Fredericksburg, and with I-95 a mere 2 miles away, you have quick access to major transportation routes.  2012 Track Circle offers a perfect combination of modern living, thoughtful design, and unbeatable convenience. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your new home! Schedule your showing today.
